data.description: Big Family Home! 4 bed, 2 bath with LOTS of updates this year. New flooring and trim, bathroom remodel, plumbing and electrical systems updated. Also features a large, eat-in kitchen, spacious dining and living room on main level, and bonus storage room upstairs. Detached two car garage/workshop features over 30 outlets (4 of which are 220 amp), a 4' exhaust fan, wall AC unit, ventless propane heater, built in air compressor, and is hard wired for speakers.  Fridge, Oven, Dishwasher included.
